          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "$120\\,\\mathrm{g}$"
        }
      ],
      "solution": {
        "translation": "石头放出的热量用于把水从 $50°C$ 加热到 $100°C$，剩余热量用于汽化。",
        "analysis": "石头放热 $1.5\\times10^3\\times0.80\\times300=3.6\\times10^5\\,\\mathrm{J}$。水升温吸热 $1.0\\times10^3\\times4.2\\times50=2.1\\times10^5\\,\\mathrm{J}$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 石头放热",
            "content": "$$Q_s=1.5\\times10^3\\times0.80\\times(400-100)=3.6\\times10^5\\,\\mathrm{J}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 水升温吸热",
            "content": "$$Q_w=1.0\\times10^3\\times4.2\\times(100-50)=2.1\\times10^5\\,\\mathrm{J}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 求汽化质量",
            "content": "$$Q_{\\mathrm{vap}}=1.5\\times10^5\\,\\mathrm{J}$$\n\n$$m=\\frac{1.5\\times10^5}{2.3\\times10^3}\\approx65\\,\\mathrm{g}$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "⑤ $65\\,\\mathrm{g}$",
        "correctOption": "⑤"
      }
    },
